    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/980640/extras/3c0abe9918bcd85475394a7f67e390cd.avif?t=1644528757\" width=600 height=174 /></span><br><br>⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀<strong></strong><br><br><strong>Empire of Ember是一款第一人称奇幻的史诗动作角色扮演游戏，</strong>融入了即时策略和管理元素，故事发生在精神前作Ember的奇幻世界。<br><br>在一次由神秘的邪教组织发起的攻击中，你的师父惨死其手，此后，你将扮演作战法师继承城市的统治权。现在，需要你夺回城市的大权，恢复往日的繁荣，为师父报仇雪恨，同时调查他遇害背后隐藏的离奇事件。<br><br>在完全可摧毁的环境中，带领部队参与多达100个战队的激战，探索布满程序化地图和地下城的世界，大展身手，打造你的专属城镇！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/980640/extras/09b6ceed32d3621da9f3498f3daede11.poster.avif?t=1644528757\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/980640/extras/09b6ceed32d3621da9f3498f3daede11.webm?t=1644528757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/980640/extras/09b6ceed32d3621da9f3498f3daede11.mp4?t=1644528757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/980640/extras/e038f3819663446160cc70ff4690aed6.poster.avif?t=1644528757\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/980640/extras/e038f3819663446160cc70ff4690aed6.webm?t=1644528757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/980640/extras/e038f3819663446160cc70ff4690aed6.mp4?t=1644528757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特点</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战斗：</strong></h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><i>在惊险刺激的第一人称战斗中使用双持咒语和武器</i>。使用近战武器向敌人发起近身攻击，挥动魔杖摧毁敌人，或者拉弓使极远的敌人爆头。</li></ul>[/b]<br><li><strong>利用环境，粉碎、绊倒</strong>、突刺或轰炸敌人。<br></li><li><strong>解开3大光明使者魔法学校的新咒语摧毁敌人：</strong>使用念力投掷巨石、抛射连环闪电、唤醒倒下的敌人，命令亡灵为你而战……<br></li><li><strong>●\t躲避、阻挡或拦截敌人的进攻，但要运筹设策，否则自己会难敌攻势！[/list]<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/980640/extras/eb86be623acb2c86e949d20a75f927fd.poster.avif?t=1644528757\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/980640/extras/eb86be623acb2c86e949d20a75f927fd.webm?t=1644528757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/980640/extras/eb86be623acb2c86e949d20a75f927fd.mp4?t=1644528757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>命令：</strong></h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>在多达100个战队的战斗中，</strong>以第一人称的身份统领军队作战。<br></li><li><strong>关键在于战术。</strong>进入战术模式，命令手下连成盾墙守住防线，部署弓箭手从上方齐发箭雨，射杀敌人。利用传送技能，潜入敌军后方歼灭对方。<br></li><li><strong>完全可摧毁的城市：</strong>使用投石机从远处摧毁防御，或者炸穿城墙，然后带领部队穿过裂罅。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/980640/extras/70fe9f6f38d5234f39adb2caacfc03e8.poster.avif?t=1644528757\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/980640/extras/70fe9f6f38d5234f39adb2caacfc03e8.webm?t=1644528757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/980640/extras/70fe9f6f38d5234f39adb2caacfc03e8.mp4?t=1644528757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>建造：</strong></h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>设计并装饰完全可摧毁的专属3D城市，守护城市安宁</strong>。部署一支卫戍近战战队守卫城门，放置战略生成点，从高塔上发射火雨。<br></li><li><strong>集成分享：下载、围攻</strong>、摧毁，以及对其他玩家的城市进行评价！<br></li><li><strong>建造设施，生产资源，</strong>助力城市的发展与繁荣。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/980640/extras/5cf344fc8295ac6edd54e837857306c0.poster.avif?t=1644528757\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/980640/extras/5cf344fc8295ac6edd54e837857306c0.webm?t=1644528757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/980640/extras/5cf344fc8295ac6edd54e837857306c0.mp4?t=1644528757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>规则：</strong></h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>招兵买马，训练部队，</strong>陪你一路冒险或驻军留守，保护城市安全。<br></li><li><strong>研究新的战队</strong>，扩充作战队，提高军队实力。<br></li><li><strong>针对子民生活中的日常活动升堂审判。</strong><br></li><li>拿定主意，作出可以改变情节，走向不同游戏结局的决定。<strong>故事作者为Telltale Games前首席作家Patrick Kevin Day</strong></li></ul></strong></li>",
